name: WIP Reject Laptops
query:
select sn.name as "Serial No:Link/Serial No:100",sn.item_code as "Item::300",sn.purchase_date as "Creation Date::100",sn.warehouse as "Warehouse::150" from `tabSerial No` sn inner join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed on sed.serial_no=sn.name inner join `tabStock Entry` se on se.name=sed.parent where sn.purchase_date>'2018-07-31' and sn.item_group='Laptops' and sn.warehouse='Final QC & Packing - Uyn' and sed.s_warehouse in ('G3 Ready To Ship - Uyn') group by sn.name 
union
select sn.name as "Serial No:Link/Serial No:100",sn.item_code as "Item::300",sn.purchase_date as "Creation Date::100",sn.warehouse as "Warehouse::150" from `tabSerial No` sn inner join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed on sed.serial_no=sn.name inner join `tabStock Entry` se on se.name=sed.parent where sn.purchase_date>'2018-07-31' and sn.item_group='Laptops' and sn.warehouse='Tech Team - Uyn' and sed.s_warehouse in ('G3 Ready To Ship - Uyn','Final QC & Packing - Uyn') group by sn.name 
union
select sn.name as "Serial No:Link/Serial No:100",sn.item_code as "Item::300",sn.purchase_date as "Creation Date::100",sn.warehouse as "Warehouse::150" from `tabSerial No` sn inner join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed on sed.serial_no=sn.name inner join `tabStock Entry` se on se.name=sed.parent where sn.purchase_date>'2018-07-31' and sn.item_group='Laptops' and sn.warehouse='Chip Tech - Uyn' and sed.s_warehouse in ('G3 Ready To Ship - Uyn','Final QC & Packing - Uyn','Tech Team - Uyn') and se.is_rejected="Yes" group by sn.name 
union
select sn.name as "Serial No:Link/Serial No:100",sn.item_code as "Item::300",sn.purchase_date as "Creation Date::100",sn.warehouse as "Warehouse::150" from `tabSerial No` sn inner join `tabStock Entry Detail` sed on sed.serial_no=sn.name inner join `tabStock Entry` se on se.name=sed.parent where sn.purchase_date>'2018-07-31' and sn.item_group='Laptops' and sn.warehouse='incoming & Dis-assebly - Uyn' and sed.s_warehouse in ('Tech Team - Uyn','Chip Tech - Uyn') and se.is_rejected="Yes" group by sn.name
